	"description": "In 2023, browser support for web components (also known as custom elements) is\nreally good. There&#x27;s never been a better time to start building your own custom\nelements.\n\nWeb components, also known as custom elements, are new HTML elements that you\ncreate. These elements encapsulate some markup, style, and interactivity. \n\nIn this article, you&#x27;ll learn the basics of web components and create a very\nsimple web component that shows the current date.\n\nThis guide is intended as a gentle introduction ",
